#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:95
msgid ""
"``column_span`` and ``row_span`` means how many tracks should be occupied"
" from the start cell. Must be ``>= 1``."
msgstr "``column_span`` e ``row_span`` indicano quante track devono essere occupate dalla cella iniziale. Deve essere ``>= 1``."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:101
msgid "Grid align"
msgstr "Allineamento nella Grid"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:103
msgid ""
"If there is some empty space, items (Widgets) in Grid tracks can be "
"aligned in several ways:"
msgstr "Se c'è dello spazio vuoto, gli elementi (Widget) nelle track della Grid possono essere allineati in diversi modi:"

