#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/chip_vendors/arm/overview.rst:27
msgid "IDE Support"
msgstr "Supporto IDE"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/chip_vendors/arm/overview.rst:29
msgid ""
"There are no limitations on the supported IDEs. LVGL works in various "
"vendors' IDEs, including Arm's Keil MDK, IAR, Renesas's e2 studio, NXP's "
"MCUXpresso, ST's CubeIDE, as well as custom make or CMake projects."
