#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/chip_vendors/nxp/overview.rst:211
msgid ""
"Extra drawing features in LVGL can be handled by the VGLite engine. The "
"CPU is available for other operations while the VGLite is running. A RTOS"
" is required to block the LVGL drawing thread and switch to another task "
"or suspend the CPU for power savings."
