msgstr "Introduzione a OpenGL"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/embedded_linux/drivers/opengl.rst:21
msgid ""
"An OpenGL context must be created before using the OpenGL driver. You can"
" create this using:"
