#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/embedded_linux/os/yocto/lvgl_recipe.rst:238
msgid "``manifests``: Track files installed in the sysroot by package."
msgstr "``manifests``: File \"track\" installati nella sysroot per pacchetto."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/integration/embedded_linux/os/yocto/lvgl_recipe.rst:239
