msgid ""
"If your ESP32 chip does not have SPIRAM you will face severe limitations "
"in render size."
msgstr "Se il chip ESP32 non dispone di SPIRAM, si incontreranno gravi limitazioni nelle dimensioni di rendering."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/libs/rlottie.rst:164
msgid ""
"To give a better idea on this, lets assume you want to render a 240x320 "
"lottie animation."
