#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_descriptors.rst:405
msgid ""
":cpp:expr:`lv_draw_box_shadow_dsc_init(&dsc)` initializes a box shadow "
"Draw Task."
msgstr ":cpp:expr:`lv_draw_box_shadow_dsc_init(&dsc)` Inizializza un Task di Disegno dell'ombra rettangolare."

