#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_layers.rst:156
msgid "Layer Buffers"
msgstr "Buffer dei Layer"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_layers.rst:158
msgid ""
"The buffer for a layer (where rendering occurs) is not allocated at "
"creation. Instead, it is allocated by :ref:`Draw Units` when the first "
":ref:`Draw Task <draw tasks>` is dispatched."
msgstr "Il buffer per un layer (dove avviene il rendering) non viene allocato al momento della creazione. Al contrario, viene allocato da :ref:`Draw Units` quando viene eseguito il primo :ref:`Task di Disegno <draw tasks>`."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/draw/draw_layers.rst:162
