"LVGL contains prepared drivers for the API of POSIX, standard C, Windows,"
" and `FATFS <http://elm-chan.org/fsw/ff/00index_e.html>`__. Learn more "
":ref:`here <libs_filesystem>`."
msgstr "LVGL contiene driver pronti per le API di POSIX, C standard, Windows e `FATFS <http://elm-chan.org/fsw/ff/00index_e.html>`__. Per saperne di più :ref:`qui <libs_filesystem>`."

