#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/indev.rst:117
msgid ""
"To prevent passing the gesture event to the parent from a Widget, use "
":cpp:expr:`lv_obj_remove_flag(widget, LV_OBJ_FLAG_GESTURE_BUBBLE)`."
