msgstr ":cpp:func:`lv_indev_read`, :cpp:func:`lv_timer_handler` e :cpp:func:`_lv_display_refr_timer` non possono essere eseguiti contemporaneamente."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/main-modules/indev.rst:681
msgid "For devices in event-driven mode, `data->continue_reading` is ignored."
msgstr "Per i dispositivi in modalità event-driven, `data->continue_reading` viene ignorato."

