":cpp:enumerator:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_ARGB8888` or "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_I2`. See the full list in the "
":ref:`Color formats <overview_image_color_formats>` section."
msgstr "Il Canvas supporta tutti i formati colore come :cpp:enumerator:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_ARGB8888` o :cpp:enumerator:`LV_COLOR_FORMAT_I2`. Consultare l'elenco completo nella sezione :ref:`Formati di colore <overview_image_color_formats>`."

