":cpp:expr:`lv_dropdown_get_selected_str(dropdown, buf, buf_size)` copies "
"the *name* of the selected option to ``buf``."
msgstr ":cpp:expr:`lv_dropdown_get_selected_str(dropdown, buf, buf_size)` copia il *nome* dell'opzione selezionata in ``buf``."

