msgid ""
"The list can be created on any side. The default "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_DIR_BOTTOM` can be modified using "
":cpp:expr:`lv_dropdown_set_dir(dropdown, LV_DIR_LEFT)`."
msgstr "L'elenco può essere creato su qualsiasi lato. Il default :cpp:enumerator:`LV_DIR_BOTTOM` può essere modificato con :cpp:expr:`lv_dropdown_set_dir(dropdown, LV_DIR_LEFT)`."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/dropdown.rst:108
