msgid ""
"By default the image Widget's width and height are "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SIZE_CONTENT`, meaning that the Widget will be sized "
"automatically to the size of its image source."
msgstr "Per default, la larghezza e l'altezza del Widget \"image\" sono :cpp:enumerator:`LV_SIZE_CONTENT`, il che significa che il widget verrà ridimensionato automaticamente in base alle dimensioni dell'immagine sorgente."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/image.rst:165
msgid ""
"If the Widget's width or height is set to a different value, the value of"
" the ``inner_align`` property (set using "
":cpp:expr:`lv_image_set_inner_align(widget, align)`) governs how the "
"image source is aligned inside the Widget."
