msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_STRETCH` Set X and Y scale to fill the "
"Widget's area"
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_STRETCH` Imposta la scala X e Y per riempire l'area del Widget."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/image.rst:193
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_TILE` Tile image to fill Widget's area. "
"Offset is applied to shift the tiling."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_TILE` Affianca l'immagine per riempire l'area del Widget. L'offset viene applicato per spostare l'affiancamento."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/image.rst:194
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_CONTAIN` The image keeps its aspect "
"ratio, but is resized to the maximum size that fits within the Widget's "
"area."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_CONTAIN` L'immagine mantiene le sue proporzioni, ma viene ridimensionata alla dimensione massima che rientra nell'area del Widget."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/image.rst:195
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_COVER` The image keeps its aspect ratio "
"and fills the Widget's area."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_IMAGE_ALIGN_COVER` L'immagine mantiene le sue proporzioni e riempie l'area del Widget."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/image.rst:203
