#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/label.rst:11
msgid "A Label is the Widget used to display text."
msgstr "Una \"Label\" [etichetta] è il Widget utilizzato per visualizzare il testo."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/label.rst:19
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_PART_MAIN` Uses the :ref:`typical background <typical"
" bg props>` and text properties. Padding values can be used to add space "
