msgstr "Impostazione degli elementi della lista"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/details/widgets/roller.rst:48
msgid ""
"List items are passed to the Roller as a string with "
":cpp:expr:`lv_roller_set_options(roller, string_list, "
