"header, with long mode :c:enumerator:`LV_LABEL_LONG_DOT` so that if its "
"text contents are wider than the area it has, the text will be truncated "
"with an ellipsis (\"...\") placed at the end of the text.  It is set to "
"be FLEX GROW 1, so if it is the only Label in the header, it will occupy "
"all available space after any Buttons are added. If more than one label "
"is added, each label will share that space equally unless its FLEX GROW "
"value is altered.  See :ref:`flex` for details about how this works. "
"Because of this, any buttons added after the last Label added will be "
"\"stacked\" on the far right of the Header."
